subject: Basketball
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Elijah Millsap had 22 points and 15 rebounds to lead U.A.B. to a 64-47 victory over No. 25 Cincinnati on Wednesday night in Birmingham, Ala., the Blazers’ eighth consecutive win.
